LogicPuzzle version 0.10
========================

LogicPuzzle - Perl extension for helping to solve brain teaser puzzles

    use LogicPuzzle;
    my $p= new LogicPuzzle (
        num_things => 5
    );
    $p->assign( { ... } );
    $p->possesions( { ... } );
    $p->verify_proc( \&my_verify );

    $solution = $p->solve();


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

NONE

